    <div class='row'>
      <h3>Objective</h3>
      <p>
        Design a mark that balances
        <strong>playfulness and credibility</strong>
        for older children and young teens. The logo should spark
        <strong>curiosity</strong>
        and signal “science,” while remaining
        <strong>clear, scalable,</strong>
        and easy to apply across web and print.
      </p>
